{
  "stem": "10098.7",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 21.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when they evacuate all the Jews I got in the one block was a gypsy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He gave me a jacket with a Polish-- political colors, red with a P.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's when I put it on, and a few days later, they evacuate the entire concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Russians were knocking on the door, so we were marching to-- to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was in that march from Buchenwald to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Took a whole month, almost.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My gosh, people were freezing, dying, every day people die.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People were making prayers over the cross, and SS been shooting them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Boy, terrible thing was going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were not Jews, just hidden Jews like myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's time when I named myself and my friends, our name [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Starkashinsky. ?] That's where I got the name [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Starkashinsky. ?] Till we got in to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Till we got into Dachau, what can I tell you?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People die like flies.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What were they dying of?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Freezing to death.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was so cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And some of them had blankets, some of them didn't have blankets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and I was really lucky.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some soldiers, we carried sacks on the back, they were tired.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'll talked in some of them for me to carry the sack.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then came [NON-ENGLISH], came airplanes, came bomb.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody run in the woods.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We run in the woods, Sol got into that sack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He ate all the candies he could, a little meat polish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Only thing I didn't eat was razor blades and soup, and throw everything away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Then when we were ready to go out, he was looking for the Klein and me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were a lot of Klein-- you know, short fellows like me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Everybody looked the same way I looked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He passed me looking for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He couldn't recognize me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "In the meantime, I had a little bit to eat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Constantly reorganizing to stay alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's the only way to stay alive, and that's what my name was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Meantime, my friend called, Stark, Stark!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, I forgot myself, who I am.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My name was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Starkashinsky. ?] You know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't change my birthday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So stupid that was, so stupid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I got in, a couple days before we got liberated, some kind of Polish organization came to the barracks looking for Polacks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They got packages, and they asked, me what's your name?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I told them, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Starkashinsky ?] from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When I was born?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I gave them-- to-- to remember that I still was in concentration camp, I said 2/2/1920.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Easy to remember, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Starkashinsky. ?] So stupid I never changed that, I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then when the Army came in the Jewish boys start looking for Jews.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I came in to the barracks with packages.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they asked me, where you get that?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, from my people, from my brothers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said, what brother?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, American Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Why, I thought you a Polack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, I'm a Jew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What you talk-- Well, yesterday you was-- I said, well, so what?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Big deal.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Get job with the leg.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'm Jewish and proud of who I am, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- and then we went for the papers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so stupid for me I never changed my-- then, when I register to go to America, work with the intelligence, and I never changed it. 2/2/1920, just-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't know, I just don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Just don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I start getting-- getting a little realized about my age when I was in America.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Would you believe that?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
